WEBVTT

00:04:59.400 --> 00:05:01.040
with a third of total capacity.

00:05:01.800 --> 00:05:04.176
There's enough for every Chinese citizen

00:05:04.200 --> 00:05:08.200
to power two homes in a single year
from hydropower alone.

00:05:08.880 --> 00:05:10.976
You may have heard
of the Three Gorges Dam,

00:05:11.000 --> 00:05:12.216
pictured here,

00:05:12.240 --> 00:05:14.486
which is the largest
power station in the world,

00:05:14.510 --> 00:05:16.016
and it's powered by water.

00:05:16.040 --> 00:05:17.376
In terms of wind power,

00:05:17.400 --> 00:05:20.456
China has a third of the global capacity.

00:05:20.480 --> 00:05:22.640
This makes it the number one
leader by far.

00:05:23.520 --> 00:05:26.456
When we look at solar,
China's also leading.

00:05:26.480 --> 00:05:30.016
